summary: Networking and communicating is my passion. As a journalist by training I enjoyed digging in new fields of knowledge, connecting with a broad range of people and tell complex stories in a compelling way. As a policy officer in animal welfare I now support those who do not have a voice: exotic mammals like primates and bic cats that end up in places where they cannot thrive.
